1
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:33,090
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:36,160
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:42,470 --> 00:01:43,800
What are you looking at?

4
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,240
Jiang Man.

5
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,830
Some people

6
00:01:51,860 --> 00:01:53,440
say one thing but mean another.

7
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,940
They talk so tough,

8
00:01:54,970 --> 00:01:56,630
but their legs tell the truth.

9
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,000
What a brilliant painting.

10
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:06,100
Wow.

11
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,090
There are way too many people here.

12
00:02:08,090 --> 00:02:11,090
They're all talking and laughing,

13
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:13,630
but why do they feel so lifeless?

14
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,920
I'll move here.

15
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:19,579
Nice move.

16
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,040
Who was that?

17
00:02:22,930 --> 00:02:24,120
Who threw that?

18
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,840
Are you blind?

19
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,680
Was that you?

20
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,800
Didn't you see me standing here?

21
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,000
Are you blind or what?

22
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:37,500
I'm talking to you!

23
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:41,640
You should apologize if you hit someone.

24
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,470
I'm sorry.

25
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:47,590
It's fine.

26
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,900
As teacher says,

27
00:02:49,930 --> 00:02:51,270
when you know you're wrong,

28
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:53,000
you must put yourself in their shoes

29
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,530
and understand their pain.

30
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,560
What you said is very true.

31
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,790
Thank you.

32
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:24,590
Class is starting.

33
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,040
Let's go.

34
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,680
What is all this?

35
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,079
Are they crazy?

36
00:03:43,290 --> 00:03:48,160
[Elite Academy]

37
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:12,840
Greetings, sir.

38
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,040
Please take your seats.

39
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,200
Everyone,

40
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,450
in a few days,

41
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,720
we'll be having another exam.

42
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,040
So annoying.

43
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,530
We just got here,
and already there's an exam.

44
00:04:47,690 --> 00:04:48,850
In class,

45
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,400
you do not speak out of turn

46
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,400
or show disrespect to your teacher.

47
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,240
You...

48
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,200
How could you just kill someone like that?

49
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,760
She was already condemned to death.

50
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:59,220
She got what she deserved.

51
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,440
Elite Academy took you in

52
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,880
to help you

53
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:04,560
wash away your sins.

54
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,900
As for what just happened,

55
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,080
just consider it her bad luck,

56
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,810
taking the punishment for you.

57
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,400
Since you're new here,

58
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,480
I'll give you one more chance.

59
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:23,800
If it happens again,

60
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,690
I won't be so forgiving.

61
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,520
You are all convicted sinners.

62
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,000
The reasons for your crimes

63
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,520
can all be traced back to one source.

64
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,670
Qin Yuren is truly cunning and ruthless.

65
00:05:33,670 --> 00:05:35,280
So what this academy seeks to do

66
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,630
is teach you

67
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:38,630
the rites women ought to honor.

68
00:05:38,650 --> 00:05:40,720
This assessment will be an essay exam.

69
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,240
You'll work in groups of three.

70
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,060
You'll each complete the exam on your own,

71
00:05:44,060 --> 00:05:45,600
but the group with the highest total score

72
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,000
will be richly rewarded.

73
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,730
The group with the lowest score

74
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,450
will be severely punished.

75
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,840
Your preferred teammates

76
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,640
can be filled in during the exam.

77
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,560
All right.

78
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,780
Class begins now.

79
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,440
Open Admonitions for Women.

80
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,720
A woman has four virtues.

81
00:06:00,330 --> 00:06:02,130
[Admonitions for Women]

82
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,640
First, womanly virtue.

83
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,760
Second, womanly speech.

84
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,840
Third, womanly bearing.

85
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:09,160
Fourth, womanly work.

86
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,720
As for womanly virtue,

87
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:14,320
it requires exceptional talent and wisdom.

88
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,520
As for womanly speech,

89
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:18,200
it requires a sharp tongue and eloquence.

90
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,370
[Strength is prized.
Women are praised for weakness]

91
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,040
As for womanly bearing, one must
always maintain a beautiful appearance.

92
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,840
[A woman must cultivate the four virtues
to establish herself]

93
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,440
I've read Admonitions for Women.

94
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,170
And it says the exact opposite.

95
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:28,150
[A woman must cultivate the four virtues
to establish herself]

96
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,320
The original book tells women
to be cautious and modest.

97
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:28,560
But her version tells women
to be bold and outspoken.

98
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:31,080
This academy...

99
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,240
Qin Yuren...

100
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,920
What exactly is she trying to do?

101
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:51,640
There isn't much more food
than on the first floor.

102
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,500
And there are so many more people.

103
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,880
Are we even going to get enough to eat?

104
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,080
One meal a day.

105
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,700
No wonder we're starving.

106
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,130
I'm getting out of here.

107
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,960
I have to fight my way up.

108
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,280
Hello, pretty ladies.

109
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,120
You're new here,

110
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,000
right?

111
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,400
You just came up from the first floor,

112
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,080
right?

113
00:07:17,810 --> 00:07:18,960
You two need something,

114
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:19,640
right?

115
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,320
We just got here too.

116
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,790
Only a few days before you.

117
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:23,720
So?

118
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,000
We're all new here,

119
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,820
so we should help each other.

120
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,980
Don't you think these people look

121
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,820
really weird?

122
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,960
They look

123
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,820
pretty dumb.

124
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,000
If we team up,

125
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,730
the exam will be a piece of cake.

126
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,840
Sorry,

127
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,240
you're a little late.

128
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:47,090
Our group of three is already full.

129
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,360
We can still help each other out.

130
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,760
You might find

131
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,040
some people are worth working with,

132
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,320
while others

133
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,640
should be left behind.

134
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,730
More help isn't always better.

135
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,920
Too many hands

136
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,180
can just get in the way.

137
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:03,240
I'm not good with strangers.

138
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,640
So,

139
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,340
I really don't like

140
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:09,000
people acting like we're close.

141
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,400
Let's go.

142
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,360
Okay.

143
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,280
Don't stand so close to me.

144
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,240
I can't stand people like you

145
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,900
hugging others for no reason.

146
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,620
Where did you get this?

147
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,600
In the last exam,

148
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,760
I got second place.

149
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,159
I got third place.

150
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,919
The teacher rewarded us.

151
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,480
Join us.

152
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,070
Good food

153
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:54,650
won't be in short supply.

154
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,860
What's wrong, Man?

155
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,680
Yanzhi.

156
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,440
Maybe you should

157
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,300
find someone else to team up with.

158
00:09:25,810 --> 00:09:27,830
I'll only drag you down.

159
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,030
This is a death match in Lingya Tower.

160
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,950
It won't be like a normal exam.

161
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,200
If it's really about
poetry, books, rites, and music,

162
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,080
then that Dao would be even less reliable.

163
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,120
Yeah.

164
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,400
You're right.

165
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,440
Yanzhi.

166
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:46,920
Then

167
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,520
you should team up with those two sisters.

168
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,200
Those two

169
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:57,080
may seem more normal than the others,

170
00:09:57,700 --> 00:09:59,470
but I'd never team up with them.

171
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,840
Why?

172
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:01,700
Intuition.

173
00:10:02,130 --> 00:10:04,260
Those two are definitely up to no good.

174
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,640
What?

175
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,570
Do you want to stay here?

176
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,240
Not really.

177
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,730
I'm just afraid I'll be a burden to you.

178
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,880
Stop putting yourself down.

179
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,440
We promised

180
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,140
we'd get out of here together.

181
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,000
Yes.

182
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:20,830
Man.

183
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:21,620
Yeah?

184
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:23,690
How did you end up here, anyway?

185
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:25,570
What kind of crime
could a sweet girl like you

186
00:10:25,570 --> 00:10:27,010
possibly commit?

187
00:10:46,050 --> 00:10:47,130
Yanzhi.

188
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,750
Do you really want to know?

189
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,040
Forget it if you don't want to tell me.

190
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:54,930
It's fine.

191
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,120
I'll go get ready.

192
00:11:02,730 --> 00:11:04,530
For tomorrow's exam,

193
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,760
I'll do my best.

194
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:07,200
Yes.

195
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:25,370
Don't be ridiculous!

196
00:11:25,370 --> 00:11:26,390
You took the blame for her.

197
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,540
Everyone in this tower
is a vicious criminal.

198
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:29,680
Do you know how dangerous that is?

199
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,520
I know.

200
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,680
You told me.

201
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:34,000
Entering Lingya Tower
means almost certain death.

202
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,400
Master was right.

203
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:38,130
Everyone here
has committed serious crimes.

204
00:11:38,260 --> 00:11:39,850
It's best to find an opportunity

205
00:11:39,850 --> 00:11:41,730
to figure out their backgrounds.

206
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,480
Know yourself and your enemy,

207
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,880
and you'll know
when to advance or retreat.

208
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,230
The academy has rules.

209
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,360
After the hour of Hai,

210
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,550
students must not
set foot outside the dormitory.

211
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:43,860
Violators will be severely punished.

212
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:44,620
Let's go.

213
00:12:44,650 --> 00:12:46,380
Come with me to see the teacher.

214
00:12:56,530 --> 00:12:57,610
What is this?

215
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,660
This is a poison gland.

216
00:12:58,660 --> 00:13:00,290
It spreads along the arm to the shoulder.

217
00:13:00,290 --> 00:13:02,190
Once the poison gland reaches the neck,

218
00:13:02,190 --> 00:13:03,180
and enters the back of the head,

219
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:04,320
there will be no cure.

220
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,120
Isn't my mother all right now?

221
00:13:06,570 --> 00:13:07,360
Why

222
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,400
hasn't she woken up yet?

223
00:13:09,470 --> 00:13:10,730
The poison in your mother's body

224
00:13:10,730 --> 00:13:12,090
has only been temporarily suppressed.

225
00:13:12,090 --> 00:13:13,850
But for her to fully recover,

226
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:15,200
and wake up,

227
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,650
we still need to find the antidote.

228
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:02,950
Yanzhi,

229
00:14:03,690 --> 00:14:04,550
stop chasing after them.

230
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:05,780
Master, they...

231
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,380
Come with me first.

232
00:14:12,690 --> 00:14:13,810
Master.

233
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:15,980
Master, what are you doing here?

234
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:16,680
While I was away,

235
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:18,200
you started acting recklessly again.

236
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,360
I suspect this floor...

237
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,640
Listen to me carefully.

238
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:22,480
Just stay on this floor.

239
00:14:22,890 --> 00:14:24,060
As for the antidote,

240
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:24,900
leave it to me.

241
00:14:24,930 --> 00:14:28,120
I think this floor has something to do
with my mother's antidote.

242
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,600
Just now,I found the same poison gland
on that student

243
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,410
as the one my mother had.

244
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:32,840
Did you find something out too?

245
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,320
Qin Yuren is meticulous.

246
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,680
If you act rashly,

247
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,810
you'll only play right into her hands.

248
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:38,560
Don't you know that?

249
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:40,280
Master, if the Tower Master

250
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:41,610
finds out you're here,

251
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:43,280
won't you be in danger too?

252
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:43,880
It's fine.

253
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,610
I happen to have important business here.

254
00:14:46,610 --> 00:14:48,020
Recently,

255
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:51,780
there have been fewer and fewer people
going from the second floor to the third.

256
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:53,640
And the death matches on the second floor

257
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:55,350
have also been getting duller.

258
00:14:55,350 --> 00:14:56,470
If this keeps up,

259
00:14:57,130 --> 00:14:59,420
it's bound to upset the guests.

260
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:00,920
You want

261
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:03,040
to put Elite Academy in order.

262
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:06,080
Ever since the second floor
was handed over to Qin Yuren,

263
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,760
I haven't interfered at all.

264
00:15:09,140 --> 00:15:10,580
If it weren't for the fact

265
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:13,620
that she can
make these tobacco paste for me,

266
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:16,240
I would never have tolerated her behavior.

267
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,930
Qin Yuren has always been arrogant
about her talent.

268
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,520
I'm afraid

269
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,760
she won't give in so easily.

270
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:26,880
She's been at the Elite Academy
for so long

271
00:15:26,880 --> 00:15:28,760
that she really
considers herself a teacher.

272
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:30,420
Then what do you mean?

273
00:15:30,450 --> 00:15:33,220
If Qin Yuren keeps
refusing to know her place,

274
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,800
then make her

275
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:37,440
just like those students.

276
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,080
This academy on the second floor...

277
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,040
Could it be

278
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:43,850
a place to test drugs on them?

279
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:44,780
Exactly.

280
00:15:45,050 --> 00:15:46,810
Then the poison in my mother...

281
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:48,560
It must have been from an early trial.

282
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,640
Now it seems

283
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:52,830
Qin Yuren should have the clues.

284
00:15:52,850 --> 00:15:53,890
Good.

285
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:55,420
That's great.

286
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,740
My mother can be saved.

287
00:15:57,380 --> 00:15:57,940
Let's go.

288
00:15:57,970 --> 00:15:59,270
Let's go find Qin Yuren right now.

289
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:01,470
You'll only alert her.

290
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:03,330
Besides, Lingya Tower is heavily guarded.

291
00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:04,600
Once the Tower Master is alerted,

292
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,430
all our efforts will be for nothing.

293
00:16:06,430 --> 00:16:09,180
Take the exam as usual tomorrow.

294
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,820
I'll find a way to help you.

295
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:12,870
As for everything else,

296
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,200
I'll handle it.

297
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,120
Master.

298
00:16:24,010 --> 00:16:26,220
[First Meeting]

299
00:16:39,210 --> 00:16:40,320
Master.

300
00:16:43,810 --> 00:16:46,540
Master, please teach me
your strongest martial art.

301
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:48,730
I want to avenge my parents.

